    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Wealth
---
Wealth is not a deterrent to self-realization or to true happiness, if
enjoyed with a feeling of detachment. ...To enjoy wealth with a feeling of
attachment is to be always aware that wealth is not permanent, as also
that, by itself, it is not the giver of true happiness and eternal peace.
